subject: Dogs
Breeding of Animals
Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show
Artificial Insemination
lead_paragraph: Improved technology has made the use of frozen sperm commonplace at the breeding of dog shows. One dog at the Westminster show was bred using 25-year-old sperm.
